name: Raging Mule
description: If you’re thirsty, ride it! Our Raging Mule packs a ginger kick that’s ready to rumble. With a splash of lime and a fizzy kick, it's a liquid firecracker. The burn smashes expectations without the next-day mule head. Get on it. Ingredients Carbonated Water, Organic Cane Sugar, Natural Flavor, Citric Acid, Monopotassium Phosphate, Sodium Citrate, Gum Acacia, Magnesium Lactate, Fruit and Vegetable Juice (Color), Turmeric (Color), Ester Gum

name: Caribbean Mojito
description: A coconut bra in a can. A minty lime carnival in your mouth, with a sparkle that dances like your dad at a beach party. One sip and you're practically on a hammock, with the surreal smell of burning grass hanging in the air. Ingredients CARBONATED WATER, ORGANIC CANE SUGAR, NATURAL FLAVOR, CITRIC ACID, MONOPOTASSIUM PHOSPHATE, SODIUM CITRATE, MAGNESIUM LACTATE, BETA-CAROTENE (COLOR)

name: Lychee Martini
description: Tame the tiger! It’s like a floral grenade, leaving behind a trail of delicate sweetness and a hint of burn. This bubbly delight is like an exotic dancer on a free bar. One sip and you’re hooked! Don’t blame us if you end up with a silly tiger tattoo – it’s happened to the best of us. Ingredients Carbonated Water, Organic Cane Sugar, Natural Flavor, Citric Acid, Monopotassium Phosphate, Sodium Citrate, Gum Acacia, Magnesium Lactate, Ester Gum, Fruit and Vegetable Juice for Color

name: Orange Old Fashioned
description: Classy meets crazy. This sophisticated sparkler pairs rich orange with bitters, a smashing twist on a classic cocktail. The subtle burn and fizz are like: elegantly reckless. Ingredients Carbonated Water, Organic Cane Sugar, Natural Flavor, Caramel Color, Citric Acid, Monopotassium Phosphate, Sodium Citrate, Magnesium Lactate
